{"tid":1658141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★睇好香港前景！】放寬樓按：將軍澳業主睇好後市","createTime":"2019-10-16T11:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T12:30:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7d0a5d0096bebff16dcd296a6909132dd5b3f9","tid":1658141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"美聯林志堅表示，將軍澳海天晉有業主看好後市轉售為租，單位為6B座低層F室，實用面積368方呎，一房間隔，今年5月以738萬港元放售，惟市況回落，8月已將叫價調減至715萬元，近日最一步減至680萬元，希望盡快止賺離場。<br />\n<br />\n隨着政府放寬按保，令市場憧憬樓市有新一輪升浪。該名業主寧決定先收租一年，以待樓市止跌回升再套現，即日以月租1.65萬元租出單位，以2016年買入價455.1萬元計算，租金回報4.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191016/bkn-20191016185004578-1016_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191016%2Fbkn-20191016185004578-1016_00842_001.html&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=8ab2d2bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191016/bkn-20191016185004578-1016_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aa4a0c578c9f35e398e600bd907e4775b9134fbb","tid":1658141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2942ed9139ba770fc33d7bd0ec8072555450ff4","tid":1658141,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89cdd9f0a079c0716745ffd37274464ba8c7ff05","tid":1658141,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor